{
  "stem": "11144.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, Zawada was a little village, really.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe the few Jews that were there were the people that were-- that my father was in business with.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We'd been to quite a few towns.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The, the one of that stands out in my mind the most was Luck-- L-U-C-K.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and in Luck, we spent, probably-- we had to spend quite a long time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I remember I went to school in Luck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in Luck, there were Russians already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was a middle-- it was a little town, I guess.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We lived in an apartment, but I, I really-- well, I-- it was, I think, a one-story, a one-story building.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was some Russian people that rented the apartment to us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I, I went to school there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there already, I had Ukrainian friends, and Polish friends, and all kinds of friends.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember that behind our apartment there was-- it was a hilly town, I guess.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It had mountains or whatever.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we used to sleigh ride.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, you know, for so a year or so, we had a normal life.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My father was working there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because, I guess he was experienced in the, in the mill.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So he did get a job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, and an uncle, one of my uncles, ran away from, from Radom, and somehow caught up with us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he was staying-- he was with us, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And, and this was-- and I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It might have been 1940.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That was still before the, the outbreak of the Russian-German war.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
